tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE ConflictResolution (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    dispute_name VARCHAR(255),
    resolution_date DATE,
    outcome VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE parties (
  party_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  party_name TEXT,
  party_type TEXT,
  party_role TEXT,
  dispute_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE conflict_resolution_disputes (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    dispute_date DATE,
    dispute_details TEXT,
    resolution_details TEXT,
    outcome_details TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE conflict_resolution_outcomes (
    outcome_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    outcome_type VARCHAR(50),
    outcome_date DATE,
    resolution_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (resolution_id) REFERENCES conflict_resolution_disputes(id)
);

CREATE TABLE Outcomes (
    outcome_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    dispute_id INT,
    outcome_date DATE,
    resolution VARCHAR,
    outcome_description VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE resolutions (
	resolution_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	dispute_id INT,
	resolution_type VARCHAR(50),
	resolution_details TEXT,
	FOREIGN KEY (dispute_id) REFERENCES disputes(dispute_id)
);

CREATE TABLE outcomes (
	outcome_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	resolution_id INT,
	outcome_description TEXT,
	outcome_date DATE,
	FOREIGN KEY (resolution_id) REFERENCES resolutions(resolution_id)
);

CREATE TABLE analysis (
	analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	outcome_id INT,
	analysis_details TEXT,
	analysis_date DATE,
	FOREIGN KEY (outcome_id) REFERENCES outcomes(outcome_id)
);
